RelativeLayout:
/* This the relative layout now we are talk about relative layout 1. Relative layout have 3 types attribute 1. Centering attribute, 2. Alignment attribute, 3.Relative to other's {@id/}
1. Centering attribute have 3/three types component this component boolean types component that means true/false 1. layout_centerHorizontal 2. layout_centerVertical 3. Layout_centerInParent
2.Alignment attribute have 4/four types component this component boolean types component that means true/false 1.layout_alignParentTop 2.layout_alignmentParentLeft 2.layout_alignmentParentRight 2.layout_alignmentParentBottom
3.Relative to other's{@id/} have 4/four component 1.layout_above 2.layout_below 3.layout_toLeftOf 4.layout_toRightOf
*/
